doc.after: In May 2009 Atlantis flew a seven member crew to the Hubble Space Telescope for its Servicing Mission 4 STS 125 18 The mission was a success with the crew completing five space walks totaling 37 hours to install new cameras batteries a gyroscope and other components to the telescope
